name: Business Rubber Stamp
description:
A lovely custom stamp with your business logo and details.

Send me your artwork for the stamp.

The stamp comes mounted on perspex and with a traditional wooden handle.

This stamp measures 2.75" inches ( 70mm) wide by 0.95" inches ( 24mm) tall.
Message me for other sizes.

I will provide a digital proof within 3 days of purchase. 

Please allow 7 to 10 days after approval for production before shipping.

name: Monogram Rubber Stamp
description:
A lovely personalised monogram stamp.

The stamp comes mounted on perspex and with a traditional wooden handle.

This stamp measures 1.18" inches ( 30mm) wide by 1.18" inches ( 30mm) tall.  

Your letter can be either in capitals or lowercase in the font pictured.

I will provide a digital proof within 3 days of purchase. 

Please allow 7 to 10 days after approval for production before shipping.
